📧 Alert System (How It Works)
🔊 Audio Alert: Plays sound when drowsiness is detected
📩 Email Alert: Sends an email to a designated caretaker
📲 SMS Alert: Sends an SMS notification via email-to-SMS gateway
⚡ Tech Stack
Python (OpenCV, Dlib, NumPy, Pygame)
Computer Vision (Face & Eye Tracking)
Machine Learning (Real-Time EAR Analysis)
Email/SMS API (SMTP for alerts)
